{"schemaVersion":"gas-shunin-manual-law-explanation-audit/v1","reviewedAt":"2026-07-11","qualification":"gas-shunin-otsu","examYear":2023,"sourceQuestionKey":"gas-shunin:otsu:2023:law:q13","questionLabel":"問13","sourceQuestionBodyText":"技術基準で規定されているガス事業者の掘削により周囲が露出することとなった導管及び整圧器に関する次の記述のうち、正しいものはいくつあるか。","sourceFile":"output/gas-shunin-otsu/questions_json/2023/00_source/question_2023_1.json","explanationPatchFile":"output/gas-shunin-otsu/questions_json/2023/21_explanationText_added/question_2023_1_explanationText_added.json","sourceCorrectChoiceText":["正しい","正しい","正しい","間違い","間違い"],"patchedCorrectChoiceText":["正しい","正しい","正しい","間違い","間違い"],"correctChoiceTextMatchesSource":true,"choiceReviews":[{"choiceIndex":0,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["ガス工作物の技術上の基準を定める省令第54条第1号"],"basisText":"露出導管の両端は地くずれのおそれがない地中に支持する。"},{"choiceIndex":1,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["同省令第54条第5号"],"basisText":"所定長さ以上の露出供給導管には危急時流入遮断措置を講じる。"},{"choiceIndex":2,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["同省令第56条"],"basisText":"高圧整圧器には漏えい火災等防止措置を講じる。"},{"choiceIndex":3,"verdict":"間違い","directBasis":["同省令第57条第3号"],"basisText":"一使用者向け整圧器の異常上昇防止装置に承諾例外はない。"},{"choiceIndex":4,"verdict":"間違い","directBasis":["同省令第58条第1項"],"basisText":"浸水のおそれのある地下整圧器には浸水防止措置を講じる。"}],"changedFields":[],"result":"reviewed_no_explanation_change_needed","sourceUrls":["https://laws.e-gov.go.jp/law/412M50000400111"]}
